# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
@angular/service-worker

### Is this a regression?
No

### Description
Trying to load the service worker file using the base-href reference returns the wildcard component defined in the routes.

## routes
`
[
...
{ path: '**', component: PageNotFoundComponent }
]
`

So assuming the service worker file loads from `domain/basehref/ngsw-worker.js`, the registration fails because the rendered `PageNotFoundComponent` is what is being returned by the route which is interrupting requests/fetches for the ngsw-worker.js file

## üî• Exception or Error
